**Privacy Policy**

Thank you for choosing to use Bluniversal Comments (“the Extension”). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect and how we use, share, and protect it. By installing or using the Extension, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

- **Extension Usage Data:** We may collect anonymized data about how you interact with the Extension, such as which features you use and the frequency of use – This goes to Amplitude and/or Posthog.
- **Local Storage:** The Extension may store settings or preferences locally on your device. This information is **not** transmitted to our servers.

---

## 2. How We Use Your Information

- **To Provide Core Functionality:** We use the Extension Usage Data to ensure the Extension runs smoothly and to improve performance and user experience.  
- **To Improve Our Services:** Aggregated, anonymized data helps us understand general usage patterns, so we can enhance and refine the Extension.

---

## 3. Data Sharing and Disclosure

- **Third Parties:** We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties.  
- **Legal Requirements:** We may disclose information if required by law or when we believe disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, comply with legal obligations, or ensure the safety of others.

---

## 4. Data Security

We implement security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction of the information we collect. However, no method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

---

## 5. Children’s Privacy

The Extension is not directed to children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

---

## 6. Your Choices

- **Opt-Out:** You may uninstall the Extension at any time, which will remove any locally stored information.  
- **Access and Control:** If you have any concerns about the data collected, please contact us using the information below.

---

## 7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated “Last Updated” date. Your continued use of the Extension after any changes indicates your acceptance of those changes.

---

## 8. Contact Us

If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: laj@lloydjones.io
